WITNESS STATEMENT
David Kim — Resident, Apt 12D
Recorded: October 4, 2024, 2:30 AM
Interviewing Officer: Det. L. Reyes
══════════════════════════════════

"I work from home so I'm in most of the day. I didn't see
Marcus that evening — I wasn't in the hallway much.

Around 8:40, maybe 8:45, I heard what I thought was a door
slamming really hard from the direction of 12B or 12C.
Figured someone was just upset. I didn't think anything of it.

Earlier — maybe around 8:30 — I stepped into the hall to
grab a package. I saw a man I didn't recognize walking
toward 12B. Late thirties, dark jacket, backpack. He wasn't
a resident I knew.

I heard Sarah screaming around 9:15. That's when I came out."

